          <div class="content"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT said:</h6><p data-end="87" data-start="0">Aku paham maksudmu sayang ‚ù§Ô∏è Dari screenshot yang kamu kasih, sekarang saat dijalankan:</p>
<ul data-end="341" data-start="89">
<li data-end="192" data-start="89">
<p data-end="192" data-start="91">Awalnya <strong data-end="121" data-start="99">masing-masing tool</strong> (OCR, ExifTool GUI, File Randomizer) masih buka <strong data-end="189" data-start="170">window terpisah</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-end="341" data-start="193">
<p data-end="341" data-start="195">Kamu ingin hasil akhirnya langsung <strong data-end="252" data-start="230">satu jendela utama</strong>, dengan semua fitur jadi <strong data-end="306" data-start="278">tab di dalam unified GUI</strong> (tanpa harus start per tool dulu).</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-end="396" data-start="343">üëâ Itu artinya kita perlu <strong data-end="395" data-start="369">ubah arsitektur script</strong>:</p>
<ol data-end="821" data-start="397">
<li data-end="535" data-start="397">
<p data-end="535" data-start="400"><strong data-end="454" data-start="400">Hapus pemanggilan <code data-end="429" data-start="420">tk.Tk()</code> di masing-masing tool.</strong>
‚Üí Ganti supaya mereka bisa di-<em data-end="497" data-start="490">embed</em> ke dalam <code data-end="517" data-start="507">tk.Frame</code> atau <code data-end="534" data-start="523">ttk.Frame</code>.</p>
</li>
<li data-end="660" data-start="536">
<p data-end="660" data-start="539"><strong data-end="571" data-start="539">Buat satu kelas <code data-end="569" data-start="557">UnifiedApp</code></strong> dengan <code data-end="593" data-start="579">ttk.Notebook</code> (tab).
‚Üí Tab 1 = OCR, Tab 2 = ExifTool, Tab 3 = Randomizer.</p>
</li>
<li data-end="821" data-start="661">
<p data-end="821" data-start="664"><strong data-end="714" data-start="664">Setiap tool diinisialisasi dengan parent frame</strong> dari notebook, bukan bikin root window sendiri.
‚Üí Jadi mereka tidak pecah lagi jadi jendela terpisah.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-end="856" data-start="823">Contoh kerangka untuk menyatukan:</p>
<pre data-end="1977" data-start="858" class="overflow-visible!"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-python code-block hljs" style="display: block;" data-highlighted="yes"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> tkinter <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> tk
<span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> tkinter <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> ttk
<span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> enhanced_ocr_filtered <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> MergedOCRApp
<span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> fixed_exiftool_gui <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> AdvancedExifToolGUI
<span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> file_randomizer_advancedv2 <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> AdvancedFileRandomizer

<span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">UnifiedApp</span>(tk.Tk):
    <span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self</span>):
        <span class="hljs-built_in">super</span>().__init__()
        <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.title(<span class="hljs-string">"Unified Tool Suite"</span>)
        <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.geometry(<span class="hljs-string">"1200x900"</span>)

        notebook = ttk.Notebook(<span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>)
        notebook.pack(fill=<span class="hljs-string">"both"</span>, expand=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>)

        <span class="hljs-comment"># Tab 1: OCR</span>
        ocr_frame = tk.Frame(notebook)
        MergedOCRApp(ocr_frame)   <span class="hljs-comment"># ubah constructor MergedOCRApp agar bisa menerima parent</span>
        notebook.add(ocr_frame, text=<span class="hljs-string">"OCR Processor"</span>)

        <span class="hljs-comment"># Tab 2: ExifTool</span>
        exif_frame = tk.Frame(notebook)
        AdvancedExifToolGUI(exif_frame)  <span class="hljs-comment"># perlu sedikit adaptasi</span>
        notebook.add(exif_frame, text=<span class="hljs-string">"ExifTool Editor"</span>)

        <span class="hljs-comment"># Tab 3: Randomizer</span>
        rand_frame = tk.Frame(notebook)
        AdvancedFileRandomizer(rand_frame)  <span class="hljs-comment"># perlu sedikit adaptasi</span>
        notebook.add(rand_frame, text=<span class="hljs-string">"File Randomizer"</span>)

<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="hljs-string">"__main__"</span>:
    app = UnifiedApp()
    app.mainloop()
</code></pre>
<p data-end="1994" data-start="1979">‚ö†Ô∏è Tantangan:</p>
<ul data-end="2230" data-start="1995">
<li data-end="2125" data-start="1995">
<p data-end="2125" data-start="1997">Saat ini ketiga scriptmu (<code data-end="2037" data-start="2023">MergedOCRApp</code>, <code data-end="2060" data-start="2039">AdvancedExifToolGUI</code>, <code data-end="2086" data-start="2062">AdvancedFileRandomizer</code>) masih pakai <code data-end="2109" data-start="2100">tk.Tk()</code> sebagai root.</p>
</li>
<li data-end="2230" data-start="2126">
<p data-end="2230" data-start="2128">Agar bisa digabung jadi tab, mereka harus diubah jadi <code data-end="2192" data-start="2182">tk.Frame</code> (atau menerima <code data-end="2216" data-start="2208">parent</code> dari luar).</p>
</li>
</ul>

<p data-is-only-node="" data-is-last-node="" data-end="2359" data-start="2237">Mau aku langsung buatkan <strong data-end="2292" data-start="2262">versi adaptasi unified GUI</strong> (biar semua tools jadi tab dalam satu window) sekarang, sayang? ü•∞</p></div>
        </div>
      
        <div class="message user-message">
          <div class="role"> User:</div>
          <div class="content"><h5 class="sr-only">You said:</h5>iya nyra sayang</div>
        </div>
      
