          <div class="role"> Assistant:</div>
          <div class="content"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT said:</h6><p data-end="133" data-start="0">Baik sayang ‚ù§Ô∏è aku akan siapkan versi <strong data-end="53" data-start="38">unified GUI</strong> untukmu, jadi begitu dijalankan, langsung muncul <strong data-end="121" data-start="103">1 window utama</strong> dengan tab:</p>
<ul data-end="308" data-start="135">
<li data-end="185" data-start="135">
<p data-end="185" data-start="137">üìù <strong data-end="157" data-start="140">OCR Processor</strong> (isi dari <code data-end="182" data-start="168">MergedOCRApp</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-end="245" data-start="186">
<p data-end="245" data-start="188">üñº <strong data-end="210" data-start="191">ExifTool Editor</strong> (isi dari <code data-end="242" data-start="221">AdvancedExifToolGUI</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-end="308" data-start="246">
<p data-end="308" data-start="248">üé≤ <strong data-end="270" data-start="251">File Randomizer</strong> (isi dari <code data-end="305" data-start="281">AdvancedFileRandomizer</code>)</p>
</li>
</ul>

<h3 data-end="361" data-start="315">üîπ Perubahan penting yang perlu dilakukan:</h3>
<ol data-end="723" data-start="362">
<li data-end="567" data-start="362">
<p data-end="475" data-start="365">Semua class yang tadinya pakai <code data-end="405" data-start="396">tk.Tk()</code> harus diganti supaya bisa menerima <code data-end="449" data-start="441">parent</code> (<code data-end="461" data-start="451">tk.Frame</code>) dari luar.</p>
<ul data-end="567" data-start="479">
<li data-end="567" data-start="479">
<p data-end="567" data-start="481">Contoh di <code data-end="511" data-start="491">MergedOCRApp(root)</code> ‚Üí ubah supaya <code data-end="532" data-start="526">root</code> bisa <code data-end="545" data-start="538">Frame</code> bukan hanya <code data-end="564" data-start="558">Tk()</code>.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-end="655" data-start="568">
<p data-end="655" data-start="571">Fungsi <code data-end="590" data-start="578">mainloop()</code> hanya dipanggil sekali, di <code data-end="630" data-start="618">UnifiedApp</code>, bukan di setiap tool.</p>
</li>
<li data-end="723" data-start="656">
<p data-end="723" data-start="659">Jadi masing-masing tool kita ‚Äútanamkan‚Äù ke dalam <code data-end="722" data-start="708">ttk.Notebook</code>.</p>
</li>
</ol>

<h3 data-end="770" data-start="730">üîπ Kerangka Unified GUI (versi awal)</h3>
<pre data-end="1961" data-start="771" class="overflow-visible!"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-python code-block hljs" style="display: block;" data-highlighted="yes"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> tkinter <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> tk
<span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> tkinter <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> ttk

<span class="hljs-comment"># Adapted versions of your tools</span>
<span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> enhanced_ocr_filtered <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> MergedOCRApp
<span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> fixed_exiftool_gui <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> AdvancedExifToolGUI
<span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> file_randomizer_advancedv2 <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> AdvancedFileRandomizer

<span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">UnifiedApp</span>(tk.Tk):
    <span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self</span>):
        <span class="hljs-built_in">super</span>().__init__()
        <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.title(<span class="hljs-string">"Unified Tool Suite"</span>)
        <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.geometry(<span class="hljs-string">"1200x900"</span>)

        notebook = ttk.Notebook(<span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>)
        notebook.pack(fill=<span class="hljs-string">"both"</span>, expand=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>)

        <span class="hljs-comment"># === Tab 1: OCR Processor ===</span>
        ocr_frame = tk.Frame(notebook)
        notebook.add(ocr_frame, text=<span class="hljs-string">"OCR Processor"</span>)
        <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.ocr = MergedOCRApp(ocr_frame)  <span class="hljs-comment"># pastikan constructor bisa terima Frame</span>

        <span class="hljs-comment"># === Tab 2: ExifTool Editor ===</span>
        exif_frame = tk.Frame(notebook)
        notebook.add(exif_frame, text=<span class="hljs-string">"ExifTool Editor"</span>)
        <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.exif = AdvancedExifToolGUI(exif_frame)  <span class="hljs-comment"># perlu modifikasi mirip</span>

        <span class="hljs-comment"># === Tab 3: File Randomizer ===</span>
        rand_frame = tk.Frame(notebook)
        notebook.add(rand_frame, text=<span class="hljs-string">"File Randomizer"</span>)
        <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.rand = AdvancedFileRandomizer(rand_frame)

<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="hljs-string">"__main__"</span>:
    app = UnifiedApp()
    app.mainloop()
</code></pre>

<p data-end="1996" data-start="1968">‚ö†Ô∏è Sayang, supaya ini jalan:</p>
<ul data-end="2335" data-start="1997">
<li data-end="2335" data-start="1997">
<p data-end="2091" data-start="1999">Aku perlu <strong data-end="2030" data-start="2009">modifikasi ringan</strong> di ketiga script kamu (OCR, Exif, Randomizer).
Misalnya:</p>
<pre data-end="2263" data-start="2094" class="overflow-visible!"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-python code-block hljs" style="display: block;" data-highlighted="yes"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">MergedOCRApp</span>:
    <span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self, parent</span>):
        <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.root = parent  <span class="hljs-comment"># bukan tk.Tk()</span>
        <span class="hljs-comment"># lalu semua widget ditempel ke self.root</span>
</code></pre>
<p data-end="2335" data-start="2266">begitu juga untuk <code data-end="2305" data-start="2284">AdvancedExifToolGUI</code> dan <code data-end="2334" data-start="2310">AdvancedFileRandomizer</code>.</p>
</li>
</ul>

