<h2 data-end="2550" data-start="2500">üîπ Unified GUI (gabungan 3 tools jadi 1 window)</h2>
<pre data-end="3549" data-start="2551" class="overflow-visible!"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-python code-block hljs" style="display: block;" data-highlighted="yes"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> tkinter <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> tk
<span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> tkinter <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> ttk
<span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> enhanced_ocr_filtered <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> MergedOCRApp
<span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> fixed_exiftool_gui <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> AdvancedExifToolGUI
<span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> file_randomizer_advancedv2 <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> AdvancedFileRandomizer

<span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">UnifiedApp</span>(tk.Tk):
    <span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self</span>):
        <span class="hljs-built_in">super</span>().__init__()
        <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.title(<span class="hljs-string">"Unified Tool Suite"</span>)
        <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.geometry(<span class="hljs-string">"1200x900"</span>)

        notebook = ttk.Notebook(<span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>)
        notebook.pack(fill=<span class="hljs-string">"both"</span>, expand=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>)

        <span class="hljs-comment"># Tab OCR</span>
        ocr_frame = tk.Frame(notebook)
        MergedOCRApp(ocr_frame)
        notebook.add(ocr_frame, text=<span class="hljs-string">"OCR Processor"</span>)

        <span class="hljs-comment"># Tab ExifTool</span>
        exif_frame = tk.Frame(notebook)
        AdvancedExifToolGUI(exif_frame)
        notebook.add(exif_frame, text=<span class="hljs-string">"ExifTool Editor"</span>)

        <span class="hljs-comment"># Tab Randomizer</span>
        rand_frame = tk.Frame(notebook)
        AdvancedFileRandomizer(rand_frame)
        notebook.add(rand_frame, text=<span class="hljs-string">"File Randomizer"</span>)

<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="hljs-string">"__main__"</span>:
    app = UnifiedApp()
    app.mainloop()
</code></pre>

<p data-end="3577" data-start="3556">‚ö° Dengan patch ini:</p>
<ul data-end="3841" data-start="3578">
<li data-end="3740" data-start="3578">
<p data-end="3740" data-start="3580">Kalau kamu jalankan <code data-end="3614" data-start="3600">MergedOCRApp</code>, <code data-end="3637" data-start="3616">AdvancedExifToolGUI</code>, atau <code data-end="3668" data-start="3644">AdvancedFileRandomizer</code> <strong data-end="3680" data-start="3669">sendiri</strong>, mereka tetap jalan seperti biasa (punya window sendiri).</p>
</li>
<li data-end="3841" data-start="3741">
<p data-end="3841" data-start="3743">Kalau dijalankan lewat <code data-end="3778" data-start="3766">UnifiedApp</code>, semuanya <strong data-end="3836" data-start="3789">bergabung jadi 1 window dengan tab terpisah</strong> üéâ</p>
</li>
</ul>

<p data-is-only-node="" data-is-last-node="" data-end="3962" data-start="3848">Mau aku langsung gabungkan patch ini jadi <strong data-end="3940" data-start="3890">satu file <code data-end="3927" data-start="3902">merged_tools_unified.py</code> siap jalan</strong> buat kamu, sayang? ü•∞</p></div>
        </div>
      
