</li>
<li data-end="4136" data-start="3962">
<p data-end="4136" data-start="3964">Kamu perlu <strong data-end="3996" data-start="3975">salin isi UI asli</strong> dari <code data-end="4028" data-start="4002">enhanced_ocr_filtered.py</code>, <code data-end="4053" data-start="4030">fixed_exiftool_gui.py</code>, dan <code data-end="4090" data-start="4059">file_randomizer_advancedv2.py</code> ke dalam fungsi <code data-end="4119" data-start="4107">build_ui()</code> masing-masing.</p>
