            <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.build_ui()
        <span class="hljs-keyword">except</span> AttributeError:
            <span class="hljs-comment"># if original method is create_gui</span>
            <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span>:
                <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.create_gui()
            <span class="hljs-keyword">except</span> Exception:
                <span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span>
</code></pre>
<p data-end="5830" data-start="5656">Jika implementasi asli menggunakan <code data-end="5705" data-start="5691">create_gui()</code> (atau <code data-end="5724" data-start="5712">build_ui()</code>), pastikan one of those is called. Jika both exist, patch to call the method that actually constructs UI.</p>

