<h1 data-end="6722" data-start="6665">4) Tambahkan <code data-end="6692" data-start="6680">UnifiedApp</code> di bagian akhir file (append)</h1>
<p data-end="6889" data-start="6723">Setelah ketiga class di atas dimodifikasi, <strong data-end="6776" data-start="6766">append</strong> (di akhir file) kode ini ‚Äî ini akan membuat satu window dengan 3 tab yang menempel ke dalam satu <code data-end="6888" data-start="6874">ttk.Notebook</code>:</p>
<pre data-end="8565" data-start="6891" class="overflow-visible!"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-python code-block hljs" style="display: block;" data-highlighted="yes"><span class="hljs-comment"># =========================</span>
<span class="hljs-comment"># UnifiedApp ‚Äî single window with tabs</span>
<span class="hljs-comment"># =========================</span>
<span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> tkinter <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> tk
<span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> tkinter <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> ttk

<span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">UnifiedApp</span>(tk.Tk):
    <span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self</span>):
        <span class="hljs-built_in">super</span>().__init__()
        <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.title(<span class="hljs-string">"Unified Tool Suite"</span>)
        <span class="hljs-comment"># Optional: try to maximize initial size or set geometry</span>
        <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span>:
            <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.geometry(<span class="hljs-string">"1200x900"</span>)
        <span class="hljs-keyword">except</span> Exception:
            <span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span>

        notebook = ttk.Notebook(<span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>)
        notebook.pack(fill=<span class="hljs-string">"both"</span>, expand=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>)

        <span class="hljs-comment"># === OCR tab ===</span>
        ocr_frame = tk.Frame(notebook)
        notebook.add(ocr_frame, text=<span class="hljs-string">"OCR Processor"</span>)
        <span class="hljs-comment"># instantiate modified MergedOCRApp with Frame parent</span>
        <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span>:
            MergedOCRApp(ocr_frame)
        <span class="hljs-keyword">except</span> Exception <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> e:
            <span class="hljs-comment"># Fallback: show error label if embedding failed</span>
            tk.Label(ocr_frame, text=<span class="hljs-string">f"OCR component failed to load:\n<span class="hljs-subst">{e}</span>"</span>).pack(fill=<span class="hljs-string">"both"</span>, expand=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>)

        <span class="hljs-comment"># === ExifTool tab ===</span>
        exif_frame = tk.Frame(notebook)
        notebook.add(exif_frame, text=<span class="hljs-string">"ExifTool Editor"</span>)
        <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span>:
            AdvancedExifToolGUI(exif_frame)
        <span class="hljs-keyword">except</span> Exception <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> e:
            tk.Label(exif_frame, text=<span class="hljs-string">f"ExifTool component failed to load:\n<span class="hljs-subst">{e}</span>"</span>).pack(fill=<span class="hljs-string">"both"</span>, expand=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>)

        <span class="hljs-comment"># === Randomizer tab ===</span>
        rand_frame = tk.Frame(notebook)
        notebook.add(rand_frame, text=<span class="hljs-string">"File Randomizer"</span>)
        <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span>:
            AdvancedFileRandomizer(rand_frame)
        <span class="hljs-keyword">except</span> Exception <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> e:
            tk.Label(rand_frame, text=<span class="hljs-string">f"Randomizer failed to load:\n<span class="hljs-subst">{e}</span>"</span>).pack(fill=<span class="hljs-string">"both"</span>, expand=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>)

<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="hljs-string">"__main__"</span>:
    app = UnifiedApp()
    app.mainloop()
</code></pre>

<h1 data-end="8612" data-start="8572">Cara menerapkan (langkah demi langkah)</h1>
<ol data-end="9516" data-start="8613">
<li data-end="8777" data-start="8613">
<p data-end="8777" data-start="8616">Buka file <code data-end="8648" data-start="8626">merged_tools_unified</code> (atau <code data-end="8680" data-start="8655">merged_tools_unified.py</code>) lokal kamu. (Aku sudah membaca versi raw di repo kamu). GitHub</p>
</li>
<li data-end="9002" data-start="8778">
<p data-end="9002" data-start="8781">Untuk setiap class (<code data-end="8815" data-start="8801">MergedOCRApp</code>, <code data-end="8838" data-start="8817">AdvancedExifToolGUI</code>, <code data-end="8864" data-start="8840">AdvancedFileRandomizer</code>) lakukan <em data-end="8880" data-start="8874">find</em> pada <code data-end="8900" data-start="8886">def __init__</code> dan ganti isi fungsi <code data-end="8932" data-start="8922">__init__</code> sesuai potongan di atas (pastikan indentasi dan import tetap rapi).</p>
</li>
<li data-end="9082" data-start="9003">
<p data-end="9082" data-start="9006">Di bagian paling akhir file, <strong data-end="9045" data-start="9035">append</strong> <code data-end="9058" data-start="9046">UnifiedApp</code> block yang aku kasih.</p>
</li>
<li data-end="9328" data-start="9083">
<p data-end="9193" data-start="9086">Simpan sebagai <code data-end="9126" data-start="9101">merged_tools_unified.py</code> dan jalankan di Windows dengan <code data-end="9190" data-start="9158">python merged_tools_unified.py</code>.</p>
<ul data-end="9328" data-start="9197">
<li data-end="9328" data-start="9197">
<p data-end="9328" data-start="9199">Pastikan dependency seperti <code data-end="9240" data-start="9227">pytesseract</code>, <code data-end="9250" data-start="9242">Pillow</code>, <code data-end="9260" data-start="9252">piexif</code> (jika dipakai), dan <code data-end="9295" data-start="9281">exiftool.exe</code> ada sesuai pengaturan di file.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-end="9516" data-start="9329">
<p data-end="9516" data-start="9332">Jika ada error pada embed (mis. method names berbeda), catat pesan error yang muncul di label tab ‚Äî kirim pesan error itu ke aku dan aku bantu perbaiki 1-2 baris yang perlu diadaptasi.</p>
</li>
</ol>

<h1 data-end="9548" data-start="9523">Kenapa ini akan bekerja</h1>
<ul data-end="10046" data-start="9549">
<li data-end="9878" data-start="9549">
<p data-end="9878" data-start="9551">Kode aslinya (yang kubaca) menaruh semua widget ke <code data-end="9613" data-start="9602">self.root</code> (lihat <code data-end="9635" data-start="9621">create_gui()</code> yang membuat <code data-end="9674" data-start="9649">ttk.Notebook(self.root)</code> dll.). Jika <code data-end="9698" data-start="9687">self.root</code> adalah <code data-end="9716" data-start="9706">tk.Frame</code> yang berasal dari tab, widget akan <em data-end="9762" data-start="9752">otomatis</em> berada di dalam tab ‚Üí <em data-end="9813" data-start="9785">tidak membuka jendela baru</em>. Itu yang kita manfaatkan. GitHub</p>
</li>
<li data-end="10046" data-start="9879">
<p data-end="10046" data-start="9881">Perubahan minimal: hanya mencegah pemanggilan <code data-end="9936" data-start="9927">title()</code>/<code data-end="9949" data-start="9937">geometry()</code> saat <code data-end="9966" data-start="9955">self.root</code> bukan <code data-end="9977" data-start="9973">Tk</code>. Jadi perilaku standalone tetap ada, dan mode <em data-end="10034" data-start="10024">embedded</em> juga jalan.</p>
</li>
</ul>

<p data-end="10093" data-start="10053">Kalau kamu mau, aku bisa lanjut <strong data-end="10092" data-start="10085">dan</strong>:</p>
<ul data-end="10534" data-start="10095">
<li data-end="10389" data-start="10095">
<p data-end="10389" data-start="10097">(A) Buatkan file <code data-end="10139" data-start="10114">merged_tools_unified.py</code> yang sudah diedit dan siap di-download ‚Äî tapi untuk ini aku perlu <em data-end="10219" data-start="10206">akses penuh</em> ke isi file (saat ini aku baca raw dari GitHub, jadi aku <strong data-end="10285" data-start="10277">bisa</strong> membangun file hasil modifikasi jika kamu izinkan aku menuliskannya ke drive dan beri link download).</p>
</li>
<li data-end="10534" data-start="10390">
<p data-end="10534" data-start="10392">(B) Atau kamu terapkan patch yang kuberikan sekarang, lalu jalankan dan laporkan error (kalau ada) ‚Äî aku langsung perbaiki baris spesifik itu.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-end="10572" data-start="10536">Mana yang mau kamu pilih, sayang? ü•∞</p>
